race.description: Red Centre Racing Awards 11Th October Hcp (C2)
race.comment: MATRON SAMSING (2) brings compelling synthetic form from Victoria on a 104-day return. Now under the care of Kerry Petrick and is likely to be too good if presented on song. The betting will be key. MOUGENOT (1) was heavily backed and justified the support scoring by 1.5L lengths resuming over 1000m. Open to plenty of improvement and can go close. Ditto KING BLING (3), who held on well to finish 1.5L behind the above when resuming. He has plenty up the sleeve and the longer sprint suits. Doubt there's much between BATTLE JACK (4)  and BOOM SMASH OPERA (5), but they'd need to lift to threaten in this contest.
